{"tid":50401,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打永遠對自己好撚無信心?","createTime":"2016-12-22T11:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T05:36:22.000Z","uid":60258,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1bbc78122585eaa2b4a35c6b6471f7adc3ef786","tid":50401,"uid":60258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:16:02.000Z","msg":"有時候自己心儀對象wtsapp自己<br />\n第一時間竟然唔係開心<br />\n而係覺得自己只係比佢用黎攝時間<br />\n<br />\n收到佢snapchat sd啲自拍相黎<br />\n有時會覺得佢只係手多多禁多左條友先會sd左比我...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時佢係fb d comment tag左我<br />\n我竟然會覺得佢係tag錯人 <br />\n我甚至走去search佢fd list<br />\n睇下有無同我差唔多名既fd<br />\n結果發現係無既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n試過一大班FD出街<br />\n佢無啦啦趁班FD睇唔到既時候<br />\n突然&quot;KIU&quot;住我<br />\n果一刻,我係好撚享受<br />\n但係返到屋企,我會諗佢係咪只係&quot;KIU&quot;錯人呢<br />\n(因為佢出街慣左&quot;KIU&quot;女仔手)<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔知點樣先唔會咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴打可以鼓勵下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:紅巴,非GAY"},{"pid":"64583886f1e8c459d6c29f2afb98708245e22cb7","tid":50401,"uid":60258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:18:11.000Z","msg":"定係我咁諗係岩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a2597430eb570d6920e930027977b81fc1fe61","tid":50401,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T11:18:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 男人老狗對自己有信心啲喇"},{"pid":"1f44394b76055e01d0b33fcde96c18863258dc75","tid":50401,"uid":65